{"tid":13733,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"你地主人點同你訓？","createTime":"2016-11-30T07:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T06:52:17.000Z","uid":5176,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b500c3eb7f691af24d2fb64e4a77860fcf4235b","tid":13733,"uid":5176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:59:04.000Z","msg":"我隻貓訓覺一定要痴住我訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大多數都係二隻手仔放上我手臂比我抱住訓，冬天通常都咁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/155726_dfd115455b9a9f6a624893dee52eb4cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F155726_dfd115455b9a9f6a624893dee52eb4cd.jpg&h=443e06fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇咁凍個時就挨住我個頭訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/155757_1debe7c4fd7a5930c972ad623de22a34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F155757_1debe7c4fd7a5930c972ad623de22a34.jpg&h=d8065f5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時仲踩撚住我喉嚨咁訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日醒都係鼻敏感流晒鼻水又眼紅眼腫。<br />\n但真係好正。<br />\n特別佢個肉球訓到暖笠笠踩上我塊臉個陣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8aa8095d8aed21a853b292191c516ffb8fe4c7","tid":13733,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:00:10.000Z","msg":"收兵post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8973cc905e67d33d7bdc0ca18fa629b0c4848cea","tid":13733,"uid"