訓<br />\n入左來又怕轉身親佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比返少少私人空間來好和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021208c504ef4676d588895b3ae9fe52c94de2de","tid":13733,"uid":32623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:59:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想同隻貓訓<br />\n自己訓上格床<br />\n下格床空既<br />\n之前隻貓太細跳唔到上來<br />\n依家大左晚晚跳上來搞住曬 訓訓下又踩你塊面<br />\n訓著左佢又要死捐入來同你一齊訓<br />\n入左來又怕轉身親佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比返少少私人空間來好和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好過我隻，肚餓先會過黎痴我，食完轉個撚頭就走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c56b2959e955501433a2182ccf7b453b6c777fb","tid":13733,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我個隻唔同我訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jda3gpth\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjda3gpth&h=69384f70&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想塞個頭入佢肚腩啲毛到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我成日都咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7defc43d518c152f51499b2e8fdb7c52a200d15b","tid":13733,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:59:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想同隻貓訓<br />\n自己訓上格床<br />\n下格床空既<br />\n之前隻貓太細跳唔到上來<br />\n依家大左晚晚跳上來搞住曬 訓訓下又踩你塊面<br />\n訓著左佢又要死捐入來同你一齊訓<br />\n入左來又怕轉身親佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比返少少私人空間來好和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解我個隻唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2622f1c6e9767beb0a2b9bccc8691cb1e188c1","tid":13733,"uid":39517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:04:04.000Z","msg":"我主人出爪爪住我心口訓 好撚痛"},{"pid":"fca6ee33468b3a69b033695b67d87786622c0f24","tid":13733,"uid":5176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:09:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我主人出爪爪住我心口訓 好撚痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同有時隻手壓住啲骨位都好痛，但佢訓得咁舒服又唔想嘈醒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2780b687ae0d6426f2792aac4f4671da65d61f80","tid":13733,"uid":19074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/170821_371a6d4d9656632d09c8cca91f36849e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F170821_371a6d4d9656632d09c8cca91f36849e.jpg&h=a9f3f37e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n瞓係我隔離，或且瞓係被入面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/171019_cb0ac3c15ffe3eb2df32e9d26c7add9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F171019_cb0ac3c15ffe3eb2df32e9d26c7add9d.jpg&h=81f7cf30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5de1e06529c4df7644850e391851686312ce5a7d","tid":13733,"uid":33376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"我果隻都好煩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夏天嫌熱就係床尾攤長黎訓，攪到我唔敢伸直腳訓，怕踩親佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家冬天就背脊貼實你塊面，再唔係成個頭搭住我手臂訓，有時重當我隻手係攬枕訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晚晚要等我訓教先肯上床訓，未訓就嘈到你肯訓為止<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/171020_d70aef43debe47ef72a864c1936644bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F171020_d70aef43debe47ef72a864c1936644bc.jpg&h=dfca715a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4aa25dcb1f72aec83ba6fb910702d5da4fafcb8","tid":13733,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔想同隻貓訓<br />\n自己訓上格床<br />\n下格床空既<br />\n之前隻貓太細跳唔到上來<br />\n依家大左晚晚跳上來搞住曬 訓訓下又踩你塊面<br />\n訓著左佢又要死捐入來同你一齊訓<br />\n入左來又怕轉身親佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比返少少私人空間來好和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解我個隻唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幻想永遠係最好 上下格床已經夠窄<br />\n加埋隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4ff6ff2aed2b33ecea048461ef65a3e0da51ae","tid":13733,"uid":39517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我主人出爪爪住我心口訓 好撚痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同有時隻手壓住啲骨位都好痛，但佢訓得咁舒服又唔想嘈醒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀我都係照訓 不過都幾暖既冬天"},{"pid":"10df3c591ee0b08729132ae48016831c4a279b12","tid":13733,"uid":39729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/185055_8cf9a0ea742bb415e84774cf5b9e6236.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F185055_8cf9a0ea742bb415e84774cf5b9e6236.jpg&h=f4e5f5ad&s={SIZE}\" /> 主人領養咗一個月，平時晚上上床訓覺時佢會跟埋上嚟，而且瘋狂煲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但係佢唔肯入被竇，唔畀攬住佢訓，只準畀隻手佢做下枕頭或者申單手畀佢攬住，好想再close啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d34dea78fe7176fac1aa5260d246b91525ae15","tid":13733,"uid":39946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:02:04.000Z","msg":"我隻貓晚晚都訓喺我頭上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae42131a8f008bfc1581af982603c69a6b79d486","tid":13733,"uid":46281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ae0635cc231b90189f85be1ef9cb4e3b9f8da0","tid":13733,"uid":15710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:05:23.000Z","msg":"絲打有冇男朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe9170cf5eecd2cc2d3f959c8770975da65b6b0","tid":13733,"uid":23463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:11:09.000Z","msg":"我兩隻聖上好乖，晚晚差唔多時間就會跳上我張床等我，有時我做緊野未瞓得，佢地會跳返去書檯陪我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我習慣側瞓，平時瞓覺就好固定一隻同我面對面瞓，另一隻就搭住我大脾瞓，唔會嘈、唔會整到我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cfa87ea1191e543b708bf259736745511e643f","tid":13733,"uid":5176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:20:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/185055_8cf9a0ea742bb415e84774cf5b9e6236.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F185055_8cf9a0ea742bb415e84774cf5b9e6236.jpg&h=86cbd3ca&s={SIZE}\" /> 主人領養咗一個月，平時晚上上床訓覺時佢會跟埋上嚟，而且瘋狂煲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但係佢唔肯入被竇，唔畀攬住佢訓，只準畀隻手佢做下枕頭或者申單手畀佢攬住，好想再close啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先一個月 再培養下感情就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7bf83f714d9bfe3ad5d0da6d39c344958e1900","tid":13733,"uid":5176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:21:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打有冇男朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8f80b230a35b753206df075cf2e453f06ea7e4","tid":13733,"uid":5176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:21:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我兩隻聖上好乖，晚晚差唔多時間就會跳上我張床等我，有時我做緊野未瞓得，佢地會跳返去書檯陪我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我習慣側瞓，平時瞓覺就好固定一隻同我面對面瞓，另一隻就搭住我大脾瞓，唔會嘈、唔會整到我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搭大脾訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁你咪唔郁得"},{"pid":"c9fad007f0f8cb2dc120b44727ad842402b264ea","tid":13733,"uid":23463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:29:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我兩隻聖上好乖，晚晚差唔多時間就會跳上我張床等我，有時我做緊野未瞓得，佢地會跳返去書檯陪我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我習慣側瞓，平時瞓覺就好固定一隻同我面對面瞓，另一隻就搭住我大脾瞓，唔會嘈、唔會整到我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搭大脾訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁你咪唔郁得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢會等我瞓著左先搭兩隻手仔上去，第二朝醒就會見到隻肥仔咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋佢兩個同我一樣超懶瞓，我起身佢地都唔願起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46aba5409a3cc5742c08c18efd412ea8372fb922","tid":13733,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/013735_60f8196165d6b89813952dcd478de920.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F013735_60f8196165d6b89813952dcd478de920.jpg&h=a9742546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朝朝起身都會見到佢係床<br />\n但佢幾時上黎我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d6b83e62b47d2733321d04c1d67dbbf2f3d001","tid":13733,"uid":1807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:48:02.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我指主人"},{"pid":"72c13464ac43d13b780ef909b316a0de147bd123","tid":13733,"uid":28628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/014826_a10f1fda11bab229b1340bad347549b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F014826_a10f1fda11bab229b1340bad347549b3.jpg&h=e2410512&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3dbe1924ede554b7a04cda2a0fde4be31ab19478","tid":13733,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T01:35:36.000Z","msg":"夜晚訓教佢自己係廳訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔洗迫住哂"},{"pid":"c5dc2e12ae7eb19fceae370de53935503eee63fc","tid":13733,"uid":3217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:23:27.000Z","ms